	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />it depends what you mean.
<br />
<br />For me the slightley higher picture quality dose not matter so a SD CRT TV sute me fine, because my interest is not haveing any lag between the game and what is displayed on the screen.
<br />
<br />If your interest is highest possiple picture quality then a high end LCD is your option. naturally you do not need a TV that can display images higher than what the machines are capable of outputing so the highest end is not nessasery. You will want a TV with a game mode so some of the picture processing can be disabled to lessin any possiple lag.
<br />
<br />If you want to be told a patucular TV there is no very best. There is a lot of competion in that market.

		

		</td>
