		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />ironfist61: Do you also plan to use this display with a home theater PC, or only for disc-based movie players and locked-down game consoles?
<br />
<br />TIP: At least on my Vizio VX32L, progressive sources (Wii 480p component, PS2 480p component, PC VGA) have far less lag than composite, S-Video, or 480i component sources.

		

